description:
Finding nearby parking locations in NYC, Boston, Philadelphia, Washington DC, Chicago, Denver, Los Angeles, San Francisco and over 50 cities throughout the US has never been easier. This feature rich app, includes a GPS based Parking Locator that automatically identifies the closest parking facilities to your exact location, an easy to use Parking Search feature that let’s you find the closest parking facility for more distant destinations or when you don’t have GPS access. We’ve also included useful information for each SP+ (SP Plus), Central Parking, or Standard Parking location including hours of operation, rates, available discounts, phone number and more. 

Top Features Include: 
*National Footprint– Parking locations available in over 50 cities nationwide including NYC, Boston, Philadelphia, Washington DC, Chicago, Denver, Los Angeles, San Francisco and more 

*Parking Locator– Find a selection of parking facilities near your exact location using GPS technology that automatically identifies the locations (on GPS enabled devices only) 

*Parking Search– Find a selection of parking facilities near a specific address you are planning to visit through custom search capabilities. 

*Mobile Enabled Coupons- For certain locations, generate a mobile coupon straight from your phone and simply show the code to the attendant for the discounted rate. (**availability varies per city and per location.)
